From 5d6ce0e37e19f957e14b798185dabe37629ab355 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: fix <fix@local>
Date: Sun, 12 Jul 2026 07:24:58 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Fix heading (section) operations: route through Things URL
 scheme

Things 3's AppleScript dictionary has no heading class, so every heading
write (create/rename/assign/move) failed to compile. Move all heading
writes to the URL scheme with database verification.
